data.clean_description: Huperzine. A is a naturally occurring sesquiterpene alkaloid extracted from Huperzia serrata. It is a reversible acetylcholinesterase inhibitor and NMDA receptor antagonist. Huperzine. A has been investigated as a treatment for neurological conditions such as Alzheimer s disease. Tags huperzine. A nootropic alsheimers dementia memory alkaloid terpene sesquiterpene.
